item.title: Weekly Review #44 - The Silent Workers, xLog and Daily Life
item.description: 'Tenderness - Mayday' Preface This piece is a record and reflection of my life from 2023-07-11 to 2023-08-15. After nearly a month of stagnation, reopening the weekly review document felt somewhat unfamiliar. In truth, many themes I wanted to write about had accumulated, and there were many words I wished to say. Although my output has decreased, my desire to share has not diminished due to changes in my life state.
